Advent of OSINT 2024 Day 3
I started by carefully examining the image provided in the challenge. The photo clearly showed a luxury property with a swimming pool overlooking a marina filled with yachts. In the background, there were dense clusters of buildings on a hillside, suggesting a coastal city with a well-known harbor.
My first step was to focus on identifying the location based on the visible landmarks. The marina, combined with the Mediterranean-style architecture and the hillside buildings, strongly suggested that the location might be somewhere along the French Riviera. I also noticed that the image had a small watermark indicating that it came from a real estate listing, which meant the photo likely existed online.
I then searched for real estate listings featuring properties with similar views—specifically, luxury homes with pools overlooking a marina in the French Riviera. After refining my search and comparing several listings, I eventually found a matching image in a property listing. The listing confirmed that the photo corresponded to a property in Cannes.
To verify the exact address, I examined the details of the listing and cross-checked the location using mapping tools and satellite imagery. The layout of the marina and surrounding buildings matched perfectly with the area near the port in Cannes.
Through this process, I was able to determine that the property is located at "48 rue Louis Perrissol in Cannes". I also noted that 50 rue Louis Perrissol is sometimes accepted as a correct answer because it refers to the same immediate property area.
